<p>Why do I get an error using this trigger?</p>  <pre><code> create TRIGGER save_Assignee AFTER INSERT ON changeitem     FOR EACH ROW      BEGIN      SET new.assignee=(select assignee from jiraissue INNER JOIN changegroup ON jiraissue.ID=changegroup.issueid)     END </code></pre>  <p>error message:</p>  <blockquote>   <p>#1362 - Updating of NEW row is not allowed in after trigger</p> </blockquote>